SOURCE_FILE@0..22
  DIRECTIVE@0..10
    SHARP@0..1 "#"
    WORD@1..8 "version"
    LINE_STRING@8..10
      STRING@8..10 " 1"
  NEWLINE@10..11 "\n"
  DIRECTIVE@11..21
    SHARP@11..12 "#"
    WORD@12..18 "format"
    LINE_STRING@18..21
      STRING@18..21 " on"
  NEWLINE@21..22 "\n"
```

